name: Corneo's Makima (Chainsaw Man) TI Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for Makima from Chainsaw Man. Chainsaw Man is an incredible series that you should try out if you haven't already.

Recommended with slight_smile or bored to really get that classic Makima expression. Oh and the clothing was excluded from training so you probably want something like white shirt, collared shirt, black necktie, black pants in the prompt to get the right uniform as shown.

As usual the eyes didn't turn out quite as good as I was hoping for despite focusing on them really heavily, so I also recommend using ringed_eyes in your prompts to try and improve on what this embed does by itself.

Example images created using my 7th Heaven mix https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
